        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉華通LEO板訂單性成長佳獲外資回補 股價周漲近14%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"華通\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:華通;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華通\">華通</a> (2313-TW) 在 2025 年營收中來自低軌衛星板的營收逾 151 億元，創新高，年增 15.27%，占去年營收的 20%。同時。華通低軌衛星板預估今年營收將再以逾 30% 的幅度大幅成長，向上挑戰 200 億元大關，近 5 個交易日獲外資回補 28778 張， 股價收在 244.5 元，周漲 13.99%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華通切入低軌衛星板時間已長達 10 年，在去年營收 759.96 億元全年 LEO 板營收逾 151 億元，創新高，占去年營收比重衝上 20% 的大關。同時，華通隨著客戶在低軌衛星發射數量的大幅成長。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-65a2a4e6-0cb4-3cc7-8016-8d23ac3d41e5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華通在 LEO 板接單結構上也有明顯改變，預計 LEO 板接單及出貨比重 ，將由目前的天上衛星板占 25% 的比重進一步提升提升 33%，等於是由 1 比 3 提升到 1 比 2，對華通的出貨毛利率的增進更有明顯的挹注及鞏固的效果。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周華通股價以 244.5 元作收，漲幅 13.99%，外資近 5 日買超 28778 張，就周線角度而言，股價呈現多頭格局，如量能持續，將挑戰月線 255 元關卡。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"華通日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hPyjTJvQY3j8pPYhOHJirg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f29bd2befccc39407daf3622b6b104b0\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">華通日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"00881鎖定高毛利AI鏈納入華通、台燿 電子五哥這2家被剔除\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:00881鎖定高毛利AI鏈納入華通、台燿 電子五哥這2家被剔除;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6426758?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">00881鎖定高毛利AI鏈納入華通、台燿 電子五哥這2家被剔除</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"全球低軌衛星需求看增 華通與燿華看LEO板出貨高速成長\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:全球低軌衛星需求看增 華通與燿華看LEO板出貨高速成長;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6424964?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">全球低軌衛星需求看增 華通與燿華看LEO板出貨高速成長</a></p></div>",
